BEST FRIEND TECH May Sales Fall 39.90% (Table) : 5321 TT

-- B y   J a n e t   O n g
-- 
2011-06-10T10:09:26Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-10/best-friend-tech-may-sales-fall-39-90-table-5321-tt.html
BEST FRIEND TECH said unconsolidated sales
in May fell 39.90% to NT$57,131,000 from NT$95,056,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  5/2011           5/2010
Sales             57,131           95,056    
YOY%             -39.90%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            319,451          383,258    
YOY%             -16.65% 
=================================================================
 